I don't do macho games.

26:55.680 --> 26:59.280
So, who do you work with?

27:06.640 --> 27:08.080
I found something.

27:09.480 --> 27:11.800
Scorpio. That's Eva's alias.

27:11.880 --> 27:13.720
Who was she in contact with?

27:13.800 --> 27:17.280
I don't know yet. But the IP address
points to the school's intranet.

27:17.360 --> 27:19.720
But it is Eva for sure.

27:19.800 --> 27:22.400
Okay. Hurry.

27:26.320 --> 27:27.240
Ruben?

27:27.320 --> 27:30.880
<i>The terrorists are not Islamists,</i>
<i>but a far-right terror cell.</i>

27:30.960 --> 27:32.320
I don't have time for this.

27:32.400 --> 27:35.160
<i>You have to,</i>
<i>or this will blow up in your face!</i>

27:35.240 --> 27:36.920
Okay. Talk to me.

27:37.000 --> 27:42.160
<i>Yathrib... chat logs... and Eva...</i>
<i>She isn't just a victim.</i>

27:42.240 --> 27:43.480
She worked with them.

27:43.560 --> 27:46.040
It's supposed
to look like an Islamist terror plot.

27:46.120 --> 27:48.960
Hardenberg is about to make
a statement in front of the school.

27:49.040 --> 27:52.160
Unless you have any evidence,
please just let me do my job.

27:52.240 --> 27:53.120
<i>Ruben...</i>

27:53.200 --> 27:54.400
Shit!

27:54.480 --> 27:57.040
-What did he say?
-Nothing.

27:58.000 --> 27:59.520
I'm going down there myself.

28:19.320 --> 28:21.200
None of our phones are working.

28:21.280 --> 28:23.320
-Sit down, please.
-What is this drill?

28:23.400 --> 28:26.840
-Why is the network down?
-It's important that we stay calm.

28:26.920 --> 28:28.400
What do you mean?

28:28.480 --> 28:30.960
Sarah, please,
it'll all be fine, okay?

28:31.040 --> 28:32.480
We can do it.

28:33.520 --> 28:35.680
We'll all get out of here
safe and sound.

28:36.200 --> 28:40.000
<i>The interior minister is on his way</i>
<i>to the Heinrich-von-Kleist School.</i>

28:40.080 --> 28:42.760
<i>He will give a live statement there.</i>

28:42.840 --> 28:48.160
<i>There are still around 1,000 pupils</i>
<i>and teachers inside the school.</i>

28:52.000 --> 28:54.920
No, it can't be done.
There's no time.

28:56.000 --> 28:57.680
<i>The minister is on his way.</i>

29:10.880 --> 29:13.400
<i>Stand by. All quiet.</i>

29:16.960 --> 29:19.040
Hey, it's going to be okay.

29:21.000 --> 29:21.960
Minister.

29:40.080 --> 29:42.320
<i>The minister has arrived</i>
<i>at the school</i>

29:42.400 --> 29:45.440
<i>and is about to make</i>
<i>a live statement.</i>

29:51.080 --> 29:54.600
<i>Mr. Hardenberg,</i>
<i>30 seconds until broadcast.</i>

29:57.200 --> 29:58.280
Helmut.

29:58.360 --> 30:00.760
<i>I checked all of Eva's user accounts.</i>

30:00.840 --> 30:04.080
<i>It appears she was in contact</i>
<i>with a guy called Thomas Tappert.</i>

30:04.160 --> 30:07.320
-Did you run a database check?
<i>-Three Thomas Tapperts in Berlin.</i>

30:07.400 --> 30:09.920
-And?
<i>-One of them works at the school.</i>

30:10.000 --> 30:12.480
-Send me what you have. Quickly.
<i>-Will do.</i>

30:15.960 --> 30:18.240
For security reasons,
we're not allowed nearer.

30:18.320 --> 30:20.760
<i>Bombs are reported at the site.</i>

30:20.840 --> 30:24.480
<i>The interior minister will commence</i>
<i>his statement shortly.</i>

30:25.120 --> 30:27.640
<i>Ole. I'm ready.</i>

30:27.720 --> 30:30.960
<i>You can proceed.</i>
<i>The others are in safety as planned.</i>

30:31.040 --> 30:33.320
Okay. The minister will start
speaking now.

30:36.000 --> 30:38.440
Get in touch
once you're at a safe distance, okay?

30:38.520 --> 30:39.640
<i>Copy.</i>

30:41.920 --> 30:43.400
<i>Okay, we are live.</i>

30:43.480 --> 30:49.200
I am here to address this situation
on behalf of the German government.

30:50.120 --> 30:54.160
I am not doing this because
I want to, but because I must.

30:54.720 --> 30:59.240
<i>Right now, all prisoners on your list</i>

30:59.320 --> 31:03.800
<i>are being driven to the airport,</i>
<i>where a plane is waiting for them.</i>

31:03.880 --> 31:06.440
<i>We will do everything you want.</i>

31:11.160 --> 31:13.880
<i>If we have somehow contributed</i>

31:13.960 --> 31:19.280
in provoking this hatred,
this anger and this violence,

31:20.040 --> 31:21.680
then we are sorry.

32:05.720 --> 32:06.720
In this country,

32:06.800 --> 32:12.400
people of different backgrounds
should feel welcome and at home.

32:25.240 --> 32:26.360
Hey!

32:32.160 --> 32:34.680
-It's me, Thomas.
-Thomas, help us.

32:35.400 --> 32:37.000
I killed one of the terrorists.

32:37.080 --> 32:39.320
We have to get out of here.
We need to get help.

32:39.400 --> 32:40.200
Take this off.

32:40.280 --> 32:42.400
-There's a bomb in the basement.
-A bomb?

32:42.480 --> 32:43.920
What about the children?

32:44.720 --> 32:49.000
Once we're out, the police can focus
on saving the children.

32:50.480 --> 32:51.640
Come on.

32:53.000 --> 32:54.320
We have to hurry.

33:03.200 --> 33:06.560
<i>In Germany, everyone has the right...</i>

33:10.480 --> 33:12.000
What the hell are you doing?

33:14.840 --> 33:16.160
Drop the gun.

33:17.360 --> 33:18.680
It's over.

33:21.000 --> 33:22.400
Who the hell are you?

33:23.880 --> 33:26.360
Asgeir knows everything.
They're on their way.

33:27.760 --> 33:29.360
You fucking whore!

34:02.480 --> 34:04.040
You deceitful cunt!

34:12.680 --> 34:13.640
You can't pass.

34:13.720 --> 34:15.960
I am the head of public safety
at the BMI.

34:16.040 --> 34:18.080
I need to talk to the teachers.

34:18.720 --> 34:22.520
Excuse me, did you get
to see the terrorists' faces?

34:27.600 --> 34:31.120
No one is coming to help you.
Asgeir was taken.

34:47.200 --> 34:50.960
We have to get them out of here.
The bomb squad needs a 1 km cordon.

34:51.040 --> 34:54.880
Hold on. Maybe we can get important
information that will save lives.

34:54.960 --> 34:57.240
This man is injured.
He needs a doctor.

34:59.720 --> 35:00.800
WE FOUND HIM!

35:03.000 --> 35:06.880
We will help you,
but we need medical attention first.

35:06.960 --> 35:08.680
He is one of the terrorists.

35:09.560 --> 35:13.040
No, they are... They are Muslims.

35:13.120 --> 35:14.000
-That guy?
-Yes.

35:14.080 --> 35:16.000
And they will blow up the school.

35:16.080 --> 35:19.440
They are not Islamists,
but a far-right terror cell.

35:19.520 --> 35:20.800
And he is a part of it.

35:36.200 --> 35:37.080
Stop!

35:37.600 --> 35:39.120
He has a gun!

35:48.680 --> 35:50.160
Don't touch that.

35:51.120 --> 35:52.400
Drop it.

35:52.480 --> 35:55.000
Drop it!

35:57.720 --> 36:00.480
<i>Let my daughter remain</i>
<i>the only victim here.</i>

36:01.920 --> 36:04.760
We have an urgent call
from the school on the secure line.

36:05.680 --> 36:07.080
Connected.

36:07.160 --> 36:10.360
<i>Ruben, you have to believe me.</i>
<i>A right-wing cell is behind this.</i>

36:10.440 --> 36:12.480
<i>The demands are fake.</i>

36:13.160 --> 36:15.560
<i>Thomas Tappert is</i>
<i>the evidence we needed.</i>

36:15.640 --> 36:19.520
<i>If we don't act, they will blow up</i>
<i>the school and Minister Hardenberg.</i>

36:20.480 --> 36:23.080
<i>We need to evacuate the school. Now.</i>

36:36.920 --> 36:41.200
Please cooperate, so we can reach
a peaceful conclusion.

36:41.280 --> 36:44.760
<i>Sir, we have new information.</i>
<i>You have to keep talking.</i>

36:44.840 --> 36:46.880
<i>We are sending in the SEK.</i>

36:46.960 --> 36:48.680
<i>It's imperative</i>
<i>that you keep talking.</i>

36:48.760 --> 36:53.840
As you know... Germany has
taken part in NATO operations...

37:57.400 --> 37:59.120
<i>Entering the boiler room.</i>

38:15.120 --> 38:16.800
We need the bomb squad.

38:24.280 --> 38:25.720
Police! Everyone out!

38:28.960 --> 38:31.360
Police! Out!

38:31.960 --> 38:33.760
Over here! Quick!

38:55.000 --> 39:01.320
Today, my wife and I lost
what was most precious...

39:03.920 --> 39:05.840
in our lives.

39:05.920 --> 39:06.880
<i>Minister.</i>

39:07.560 --> 39:09.920
<i>We have the situation under control.</i>

39:21.560 --> 39:22.800
Yeah.

39:23.640 --> 39:25.320
We're compromised.

39:25.400 --> 39:27.520
The police came.
They nearly killed me.

39:27.600 --> 39:29.760
And I can't get ahold of Ole.

39:29.840 --> 39:31.240
<i>I think the police got him.</i>

39:31.320 --> 39:33.280
-Where are you?
<i>-I don't know.</i>

39:33.360 --> 39:36.080
In some street. Hiding.

39:36.160 --> 39:38.560
<i>I'll find a safe place</i>
<i>for us to meet.</i>

39:38.640 --> 39:41.040
I'll send you details.
Stay out of sight.

39:52.800 --> 39:54.320
<i>Where is the world heading?</i>

39:55.160 --> 39:57.800
<i>Depends on how we define ourself.</i>

39:58.320 --> 40:00.760
<i>By the darkness</i>
<i>we've allowed too long?</i>

40:01.680 --> 40:04.400
<i>Or by our will</i>
<i>to protect the light?</i>

40:05.720 --> 40:09.800
<i>I hope my darkest deeds</i>
<i>will not define my true self.</i>

40:09.880 --> 40:11.000
<i>Or us.</i>

40:31.920 --> 40:33.800
<i>They wanted to change us all.</i>

40:34.880 --> 40:36.560
<i>Not just an election.</i>

40:38.440 --> 40:42.840
<i>History will judge how we all act</i>
<i>when our world is coming apart.</i>

40:45.320 --> 40:47.520
<i>Did you save yourself?</i>

40:47.600 --> 40:49.720
<i>Or did you try to save others?</i>

40:55.240 --> 40:58.720
<i>What thoughts and deeds</i>
<i>do you allow to shape your life?</i>

40:58.800 --> 41:02.400
<i>Shape our future? Shape ourself?</i>

41:03.720 --> 41:04.960
<i>Can you heal?</i>

41:06.480 --> 41:07.680
<i>Can I?</i>

41:20.960 --> 41:22.440
So what's the plan now?

41:22.520 --> 41:24.400
Ole and I didn't agree
on everything.

41:25.120 --> 41:29.080
However, we won't win
without a voice.

41:32.800 --> 41:34.200
Anyway...

41:34.280 --> 41:38.120
This group isn't the only one
that answers to Cato.

41:38.720 --> 41:42.280
So even if the cops killed Ole,
it won't stop us.

41:42.880 --> 41:45.000
The plan is to keep Cato alive.

41:45.600 --> 41:48.680
And that's where Furia
and your talent for words comes in.

41:48.760 --> 41:52.160
Okay. What do we need him for?

41:52.240 --> 41:54.080
He knows how the cops found us.

41:54.160 --> 41:57.800
And he knows something
the Russians want to know as well.

42:10.400 --> 42:12.560
What other cells?

42:12.640 --> 42:14.360
I can't say I'm surprised.

42:14.440 --> 42:17.120
What other cells?

42:25.040 --> 42:26.480
You're bluffing.

42:27.600 --> 42:28.440
Move.

42:31.600 --> 42:32.720
Get down.

42:36.520 --> 42:38.320
You were going to kill kids.

42:39.440 --> 42:40.560
Like my sister.

42:40.640 --> 42:43.440
I'm pretty sure
I never killed any Norwegian girl.

42:43.520 --> 42:45.160
Shut the fuck up.

42:47.800 --> 42:49.400
He has a knife. Come here.

42:50.200 --> 42:51.560
Okay, cut me loose.

43:02.680 --> 43:05.160
Let me borrow your phone.
I have to call Michelle.

43:05.240 --> 43:07.040
Of course. Here.

43:10.560 --> 43:12.760
Hello. Hi, are you with her now?

43:13.360 --> 43:14.800
Okay. Good.

43:14.880 --> 43:18.920
Take her somewhere safe
and get someone to protect you.

43:19.000 --> 43:20.040
Yes.

43:22.040 --> 43:23.240
I'm coming home.

43:26.560 --> 43:28.840
-Did you call the cops?
-Of course.

43:30.920 --> 43:35.080
<i>I think what we need now is a...</i>

43:36.800 --> 43:38.960
cross-party statement.

43:40.560 --> 43:42.760
Devoid of any
political self-interest.

43:44.480 --> 43:48.320
Germany needs to know the truth
about these attacks. Right away.

43:55.000 --> 43:58.120
You need to know
that I had help from Norway.

43:59.280 --> 44:01.880
This has to remain top secret.

44:01.960 --> 44:04.440
The identities need to be protected.

44:08.240 --> 44:10.600
This is far from over.

44:17.320 --> 44:18.880
<i>Truth.</i>

44:18.960 --> 44:20.400
<i>I'm like you.</i>

44:20.480 --> 44:24.040
<i>Afraid of the future,</i>
<i>because of the past.</i>

44:27.080 --> 44:30.240
<i>Few know the true darkness</i>
<i>of what I've done.</i>

44:31.480 --> 44:33.720
<i>Or if I can ask for forgiveness.</i>

44:40.200 --> 44:41.320
<i>I know this:</i>

44:42.200 --> 44:44.160
<i>The darkness isn't gone.</i>

44:46.320 --> 44:50.320
<i>This isn't over,</i>
<i>though I will be gone for a while.</i>

44:52.120 --> 44:55.320
<i>These are my last words... for now.</i>

44:56.680 --> 44:58.200
<i>Furia.</i>

45:03.080 --> 45:06.360
Subtitles: Aleksander Kerr
